    <div class="About">
        <h3>Introduction:</h3>
        <p>Welcome to Dose Pharmacy, your trusted healthcare partner. We have been serving this community since 2023, providing personalized and efficient pharmaceutical services to meet your health and wellness needs.</p>
        <h3>Mission:</h3>
        <p>Our mission is to prioitize patient care and satisfaction, ensuring a seamless experience for everyone who walks through our doors. We are committed to delivering high-quality medications, expert advice, and exceptional service.</p>
        <h3>Values:</h3>
        <p>At Dose Pharmacy, we are guided by the following core values:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Integrity: We adhere to the highest ethical standards and maintain transparency in all our interactions.</li>
                <li>Professionalism: Our team consists of experienced pharmacists and staff who prioritize continuous learning and development to stay up-to-date with industry advancements.</li>
                <li>Compassion: We empathize with our patients and strive to create a welcoming environment where everyone feels valued and cared for.</li>
