        <p>Dose Pharmacy offers a wide range of pharmaceutical services, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Prescription Medication Dispensing: We provide a vast selection of prescription medications, ensuring accuracy and safety in every order.</li>
                <li>Over-the-Counter (OTC) Products: Our shelves are stocked with a variety of OTC medications, health supplements, and personal care products to cater to your wellness needs.</li>
                <li>Medication Counseling: Our pharmacists are always available to discuss your medications, dosage instructions, potential side effects, and answer any questions you may have.</li>
